(24, 1, '', 2, 'Ngoại truyện (1)', 'ngoai-truyen-1-', '<h1 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:21.333333333333332px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ngoại truyện</span></h1><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ngoại truyện Tiểu Sư x Tiểu Bình:</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tết Trung thu Tiểu Bình dắt tay Tiểu Sư đi dạo trên phố. Tới một cửa hàng đồ chơi, Tiểu Sư bất giác dừng lại, dí sát mặt vào kính, nhìn chằm chằm đôi tai thỏ.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tiểu Sư, "Cái kia... Đẹp nhỉ?!"</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tiểu Bình cười hiền, xoa xoa đầu Tiểu Sư, "Đẹp! Em đeo sẽ rất đáng yêu!"</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tiểu Sư: "Ý em là cho anh."</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tiểu Bình: "..."</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">----------------------------------------------</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ngoại truyện Mã Mã x Tiểu Bạch:</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">(Bạch Dương là tên bạn tr